        <br />
        <div class="UserSuppliedContent">
            
            <span id="ctl00_ContentBody_LongDescription"><center><img src="http://img.geocaching.com/cache/9959bd62-c91f-45f5-947c-3e4aaa1e98f8.jpg" width="134" height="226" alt="krizek" /></center>
<p align="center" style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="6"><b>Geocaching jinak</b></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>S geocachingem to jde posledni dobou z kopce.</i></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- V mediich se objevuje stale casteji.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Zkousi se mu venovat vic a vic lidi.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Nove kese rostou jak houby po desti, a hodne z nich nestoji za vic nez za bod.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Mnozi se pokusy o publikovani kontroverznich kesi s pozadavkem na precedent.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Ignore listy se plni mysterkami typu: na co autor myslel pri kodovani souradnic.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Stare (kvalitni) kese se ztraceji, ci byvaji vymudleny.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Coiny a TB se ztraceji spolu s kesemi, nebo jsou z nich cilene vybirany.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- A tak dale......doplnte sami</i></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><b>A prave temto ztracenym sigitemum je urcena tato cache. (TB/GC hrbitov)</b></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Sem muzete pomoci "WN" umistit svuj ztraceny Coin ci TB.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Ti, co si ji budou chtit najit a zalogovat "Found It", musi zvladnout nasledujici ukol:</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>Cesky jazyk obsahuje asi 190 tisíc slov (Slovnik spisovneho jazyka ceskeho 1989). Ale jenom jedno se jinak pise a jinak cte. Na rozdil treba od anglickeho jazyka, kde se snad vsechna slova jinak pisi a jinak ctou.</i></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>Toto slovo najdete a prevedte ho do Morseovy abecedy (tecky, carky) .</i></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Cache najdete na souradnicich:<br /></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><br /></font></p>
<font size="4"><font size="6"><b>N 49° 0A.BCD<br />
E 017° 3E.FGH</b></font></font>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Kde:</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">A = pocet vsech znaku v prvnim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">B = pocet vsech znaku v druhem, ctvrtem a poslednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">C = pocet carek v prvnim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">D = pocet tecek ve druhem a predposlednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">E = pocet vsech znaku ve tretim a predposlednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">F = pocet carek v prvnim a poslednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">G = B</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">H = pocet tecek ve tretim a poslednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Schranka je micro zamerne.<br /></font></p>
<center><font size="4">Souradnice si overte zde.</font></center>

        var latMin = $('#ctl00_ContentBody_txtLatMinutes');
        var lonMin = $('#ctl00_ContentBody_txtLongMinutes');

        // check direction values
        var latitudeError = $('#lblLatitudeError');
        var longitudeError = $('#lblLongitudeError');
        var latDirError = !latDirection || (latDirection.val().toUpperCase() !== "N" && latDirection.val().toUpperCase() !== "S");
        var lonDirError = !lonDirection || (lonDirection.val().toUpperCase() !== "W" && lonDirection.val().toUpperCase() !== "E");
        var latDegError = !latDeg || !$.isNumeric(latDeg.val());
        var latMinError = !latMin || !$.isNumeric(latMin.val());
        var lonDegError = !lonDeg || !$.isNumeric(lonDeg.val());
        var lonMinError = !lonMin || !$.isNumeric(lonMin.val());
        var hasError = false;

        latDeg.removeClass("error-field");
        latMin.removeClass("error-field");
        latDirection.removeClass("error-field");
        latitudeError.text("");

        if (latDegError || latMinError || latDirError) {
            if (latDegError) {
                latDeg.addClass("error-field");
                latitudeError.text("Degrees and minutes must be numeric.");
            }

            if (latMinError) {
                latMin.addClass("error-field");
                latitudeError.text("Degrees and minutes must be numeric.");
            }
            
            if (latDirError) {
                latDirection.addClass("error-field");
                latitudeError.text("Latitude direction must be N or S");
            }

            hasError = true;
            latitudeError.show();
        }

        lonDeg.removeClass("error-field");
        lonMin.removeClass("error-field");
        lonDirection.removeClass("error-field");
        longitudeError.text("");

        if (lonDegError || lonMinError || lonDirError) {
            if (lonDegError) {
                lonDeg.addClass("error-field");
                longitudeError.text("Degrees and minutes must be numeric.");
            }

            if (lonMinError) {
                lonMin.addClass("error-field");
                longitudeError.text("Degrees and minutes must be numeric.");
            }

            if (lonDirError) {
                lonDirection.addClass("error-field");
                longitudeError.text("Longitude direction must be E or W");
            }
            
            longitudeError.show();
            hasError = true;
        }

        if (hasError) {
            var solutionResponse = $('#lblSolutionResponse');
            solutionResponse.removeClass("solution-error");
            solutionResponse.text("");
            return false;
        }

        var north = latDirection.val().toUpperCase() == "N";
        var east = lonDirection.val().toUpperCase() == "E";

        var recaptcha = "";
        var recaptchaElement = $('#g-recaptcha-response');
        if (recaptchaElement && recaptchaElement.val()) {
            recaptcha = recaptchaElement.val();
        }

        var data = {'coord' : {
            'LatDir' : latDirection.val(), 'LonDir' : lonDirection.val(), 'LatMin' : latMin.val(),
            'LonMin' : lonMin.val(), 'LatDeg' : latDeg.val(), 'LonDeg' : lonDeg.val(),
            'North' : north, "East" : east
        }, 'recaptcha' : recaptcha, 'ut' : userToken  }

        $.ajax({
            type: "POST",
            url: "/seek/cache_details.aspx/CheckCoordsButton",
            data: JSON.stringify(data),
            contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
            dataType: "json",
            error: function (XMLHttpRequest, textStatus, errorThrown) {
                var textResult = $('#lblSolutionResponse');
                textResult.text('Solution checker failed. Please try again later.');
                textResult.addClass("solution-error");
                textResult.removeClass("solution-success");
            },
            success: function(result) {
                var response = JSON.parse(result.d);
                var textResult = $('#lblSolutionResponse');

                if (response.Success == false) {
                    textResult.addClass("solution-error");

                    if (!response.Verified) {
                        textResult.text("Recaptcha validation failed.");
                        $('#recaptcha-br').show();
                        $('.g-recaptcha').show();
                    } else if (!response.FinalCoordsListed) {
                        textResult.text("No final coordinates have been given for this geocache.");
                    } else if (response.AttemptsLeft == 1) {
                        textResult.text("Those coordinates are not correct. You have 1 try left.");
                    } else if (response.AttemptsLeft > 1) {
                        var attempts = 0;
                        if (response.AttemptsLeft > 1) {
                            attempts = response.AttemptsLeft;
                        }
                        var text = "Those coordinates are not correct. You have {0} tries left.".replace("{0}", attempts);
                        textResult.text(text);
                    } else {
                        textResult.text("You have 0 tries left. Try again in 10 minutes.");
                    }

                    if (response.Verified) {
                        $('#recaptcha-br').hide();
                        $('.g-recaptcha').hide();
                    }
                } else {
                    textResult.removeClass("solution-error");
                    textResult.addClass("solution-success");

                    var latSolution = latDirection.val().toUpperCase() +
                        " " +
                        latDeg.val() +
                        String.fromCharCode(176) +
                        " " +
                        latMin.val() +
                        "\'";
                    var lonSolution = lonDirection.val().toUpperCase() +
                        " " +
                        lonDeg.val() +
                        String.fromCharCode(176) +
                        " " +
                        lonMin.val() +
                        "\'";
                    $('#solution-lat').text(latSolution);
                    $('#solution-lon').text(lonSolution);

                    textResult.text("Correct! The coordinates for this cache have been updated.");

                    if (response.Distance != "") {
                        var correctCoords = $('#uxLatLon');
                        correctCoords.addClass("myLatLon");
                        correctCoords.text(response.CorrectedCoords);

                        $('#ctl00_ContentBody_LocationSubPanel').text("UTM: " + response.Utm);

                }
            }
        });

        function setStaticMap() {

                zoom: 14,
                doubleClickZoom: true,
                dragging: true,
                touchZoom: false,
                scrollWheelZoom: false,
                zoomControl: true,
                attributionControl: false
            })
            .addControl(new L.Control.Attribution({ prefix: '© <a href="http://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright" target="_blank">OpenStreetMap</a> contributors. <a href="/about/maps.aspx#leaflet" target="_blank">About our maps</a>' }))
            .addControl(new L.Control.Scale());

            addInternalMapTileLayer(mapLarge, function(layer) {
                if (cmapAdditionalWaypoints != null && cmapAdditionalWaypoints.length > 0) {

                    var llBounds = L.latLngBounds([mapLatLng.lat, mapLatLng.lng], [mapLatLng.lat, mapLatLng.lng]);

                    for (var x = 0, len = cmapAdditionalWaypoints.length; x < len; x++) {

                        var item = cmapAdditionalWaypoints[x],
                            ll = [item.lat, item.lng];

                        L.marker(ll, {
                            icon:  L.icon({ iconUrl: '/images/wpttypes/pins/'+ item.type + '.png', iconSize: [20, 23], iconAnchor: [10, 23] }),
                            title: item.name,
                            clickable: false
                        }).addTo(mapLarge);

                        llBounds.extend(ll);
                    }

                    window.setTimeout(function () {
                        mapLarge.fitBounds(llBounds.pad(.5));
                    }, 100);
                }

                // Add posted coords last so they are prioritized on map
                L.marker([mapLatLng.lat, mapLatLng.lng], {
                    icon: L.icon({iconUrl: '/images/wpttypes/pins/' + mapLatLng.type + '.png', iconSize: [20, 23], iconAnchor: [10, 23]}),

                    title: mapLatLng.name
                }).addTo(mapLarge);
            });
